GetPrices()
AddMenuItem()
RemoveMenuItem()
CloseRestaurant()
OpenRestaurant()
CancelOrder()
AcceptOrder()

Class Name: Payment

Description of Class:
The process of paying for user’s order

Class Attributes
Price: int
BankInfo: String
Bank#: int

Class Operations:
AddCard()
AddBank()
ShowPrice()
GiveReceipt()
GiveTip()


